{"tid":1193493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"預計3點過後，三毛開始反Cup時事台，大家提防謠言","createTime":"2019-06-09T02:42:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T04:20:19.000Z","uid":90735,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"820818ee72f633fee971b7effc1478cc1ec4f0cf","tid":1193493,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T02:42:06.000Z","msg":"呢幾日三毛輿論戰完全打輸晒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好耐未見過大家咁同心合力<br />\n<br />\n但係3點過後，多咗人出咗去遊行之後，預料三毛開始反cup<br />\n根據呢個正負評，常駐三毛大概30幾個，足以影響成個討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1192602/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1192602/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>大家提防所有謠言<br />\n記住<br />\n所謂「警察朋友嘅內幕消息」<br />\n做得警察嘅都斷六親，朋友得返警察同事<br />\n所以聲稱朋友係警察嘅人<br />\n好大機會一係藍絲，一係本身都係警察<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\nWhatsapp group 傳嚟所謂「朋友消息」<br />\n記得問清楚係邊個朋友先<br />\n唔好亂轉發「朋友消息」<br />\n朋友係識得嘅，越接近原source越可信<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n遲出去嘅或者喺外國嘅朋友繼續打輿論戰"},{"pid":"4e0612e05d6de42bbaece55767a6358a0cb01e78","tid":1193493,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T02:42:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/PoliticalVigorousHousefly-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FPoliticalVigorousHousefly-size_restricted.gif&h=41e34efc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jfok9qw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjfok9qw.png&h=2447e81f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"053c245ab66ffdab65f570d9e6d0ea9a7757146f","tid":1193493,"uid":88123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T02:42:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b541ee6e25597336cb29ff159c0902fab75df9","tid":1193493,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T02:43:56.000Z","msg":"記住，任何相，任何謠言，唔好第一時間forward<br />\n就算坦克車真係入緊城你都避唔切，等十五分鐘應該有人會澄清到"},{"pid":"cfb5c4c98a9d2995527d484878f99f5bba5aa664","tid":1193493,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T02:44:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />事關香港歷史之重大變局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我想借大家少少位用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望大家可以原諒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jOPvJL6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjOPvJL6.png&h=344452d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">阻止惡法！為時未晚！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【民陣6.9反惡法遊行】 <br />\n<br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n<br />\n集合地點：<span style=\"color: red;\">銅鑼灣維多利亞公園中央草坪 （維園草地）</span><br />\n<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步<br />\n<br />\n遊行路線：維園草地起點&gt;高士威道&gt; 禮頓道&gt;伊榮街&gt;邊寧頓街&gt;軒尼詩道西行車路&gt;金鐘道&gt;樂禮街&gt;夏愨道&gt;添美道&gt;立法會外行人路終點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n百國聯軍助陣！感謝海外港人為香港人嘅未來而作出嘅努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AG0SmhW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAG0SmhW.png&h=5d5fe630&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>愛因斯坦 (Albert Einstein)：「The world will not be destoryed by those who do evil, but by these who watch them without doing anything.(這個世界不會被那些作惡多端的人毀滅，而是冷眼旁觀、選擇保持緘默的人)」；鄭有傑(導演):「良心的沉默是邪惡的幫兇。」<br />\n<br />\n好多時歷史中嘅轉折位都係由表面上微不足道嘅小事/小人物而形成嘅，所以我地更加唔可以睇小自己</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a051c5f5637